    <!-- Prototype Section -->
    <section id="prototype" class="container-fluid content-section text-center">
            <% include ../partials/match-diagram.ejs -%>
    </section>

    <!-- Request A Match Section -->
    <section id="input-match-id" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h1>Request A Match</h1>

                <p> If there is a particular match you would like to see analysed you can add it to the queue via the following link:</p>

                <a href="http://goo.gl/forms/6UZBwulPbn" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Match ID</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


	<!-- About Prototype Section -->
	<section id="about-prototype" class="container content-section text-center">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h1> About The Prototype </h1>

                <p> This is an early-stage protoype for an application that will take in replays and automatically generate an overview of the gameplay. The idea is to allow you to review a game quickly and focus on the important aspects without having to watch the whole replay.</p>

                <p>Above you can see the final game of the Frankfurt Major, Team Secret vs. OG Game 4 - processed using the current version of our software.
                </p>
                <p> The project is still obviously a work in progress - with lots more features planned - so stay tuned for updates and let us know if you have any feedback! </p>

        <p> You can log in with your Steam accout to get on the platform and see all the other games we have parsed so far. In the coming days we will fully automate the analysis and allow users signed up for our beta to upload and analyse games themself!</p>

                <a href="http://goo.gl/forms/Nb6S8eGaCm" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Beta Sign Up</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h2>Contact Wisdota</h2>
                <p>We would love to hear how we can improve our prototype and what you want to see from us. Please fill out our short feedback form: </p>
                <a href="http://goo.gl/forms/vfHqGGvybU" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Feedback Form</a>
                <p id="more-margin">Or you can find us on Twitter:</p>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/wisdota" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-fw"></i><span class="network-name">Twitter</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


